---
// DatabaseSlide.astro - Slide para Gestión y Administración de Bases de Datos
---

<div class="database-card">
    <div class="card-content">
      <!-- Panel de información -->
      <div class="info-panel">
        <div class="service-header">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse>
              <path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"></path>
              <path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"></path>
            </svg>
            <div class="icon-pulse"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="service-title">GESTIÓN DE BASES DE DATOS</h3>
        </div>
        
        <p class="service-description">
          Diseñamos, implementamos y optimizamos soluciones de almacenamiento de datos SQL y NoSQL, garantizando rendimiento, seguridad y escalabilidad para gestionar eficientemente grandes volúmenes de información.
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-features">
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">SQL</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 7 12 3 3 7l9 4 9-4Z"></path>
                <path d="m21 13-9-4-9 4 9 4 9-4Z"></path>
                <path d="m21 19-9-4-9 4 9 4 9-4Z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">NoSQL</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10H12V2Z"></path>
                <path d="M21.2 8A10 10 0 0 0 17.6 4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">Optimización</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-tags">
          <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="tag">MongoDB</span>
          <span class="tag">Redis</span>
          <span class="tag">Data Modeling</span>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/servicios/database" class="service-link">
          <span class="link-text">Conocer más</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
            <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <style>
    /* Variables y estilos base */
    .database-card {
      --slide-color: var(--aqua);
      --highlight-color: #42e8ff;
      --lowlight-color: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.5);
      --bg-glow: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.1);
      --text-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      --border-color: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.3);
      
      width: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    .card-content {
      background: rgba(26, 20, 45, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 0 30px rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.1);
    }
    
    .card-content::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, var(--bg-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    /* ===== Panel de información ===== */
    .info-panel {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .service-header {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .service-icon {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.1);
      border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--highlight-color);
      position: relative;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .service-icon svg {
      width: 35px;
      height: 35px;
    }
    
    .icon-pulse {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 2px solid var(--highlight-color);
      opacity: 0;
      z-index: -1;
      animation: icon-pulse 2s infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes icon-pulse {
      0% {
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
        opacity: 0.7;
      }
      100% {
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.5);
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }
    
    .service-title {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--highlight-color);
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 2px rgba(20, 20, 40, 0.4),
        0 0 8px var(--highlight-color);
      animation: subtle-glow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .service-title::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--highlight-color), transparent);
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 0;
      animation: line-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes subtle-glow {
      from {
        text-shadow: 
          0 0 2px rgba(20, 20, 40, 0.4),
          0 0 8px var(--highlight-color);
      }
      to {
        text-shadow: 
          0 0 2px rgba(20, 20, 40, 0.6),
          0 0 12px var(--highlight-color);
      }
    }
    
    @keyframes line-pulse {
      0%, 100% {
        opacity: 0.3;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--highlight-color);
      }
      50% {
        opacity: 0.8; 
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--highlight-color);
      }
    }
    
    .service-description {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-color);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    /* Features con iconos */
    .service-features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .feature {
      background: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .feature:hover {
      background: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.1);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      width: 35px;
      height: 35px;
      color: var(--highlight-color);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .feature-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    }
    
    /* Etiquetas */
    .service-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .tag {
      background: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-color);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .tag:hover {
      background: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.2);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.3);
    }
    
    /* Enlace de servicio */
    .service-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background: rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      color: var(--highlight-color);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: auto;
    }
    
    .service-link::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
      transition: left 0.5s ease;
    }
    
    .service-link:hover {
      background: var(--highlight-color);
      color: rgba(20, 20, 40, 1);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 0 10px rgba(66, 232, 255, 0.5);
    }
    
    .service-link:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }
    
    .service-link svg {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .service-link:hover svg {
      transform: translateX(5px);
    }
    
    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .card-content {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      .service-title {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
      }
      
      .service-description {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      
      .service-features {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 0.75rem;
      }
      
      .feature-icon {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
      }
      
      .feature-text {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .card-content {
        padding: 1.25rem;
      }
      
      .service-icon {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }
      
      .service-icon svg {
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
      }
      
      .service-title {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }
      
      .service-description {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      .service-features {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
      
      .tag {
        padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
      
      .service-link {
        padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 400px) {
      .service-features {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 0.7rem;
      }
    }
  </style>